187
00:19:39.641 --> 00:19:40.681
Grazie.

188
00:19:40.801 --> 00:19:43.001
La vraie chose.

189
00:19:43.201 --> 00:19:43.881
Cosa?

190
00:19:44.041 --> 00:19:45.001
E
-Era francese?

191
00:19:55.242 --> 00:19:56.762
